<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْكِتَابَ}</span> ... التَّوْرَاةَ، وَالإِنْجِيلَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُرِيبٍ}</span> ... مُوقِعٍ فِي الرِّيبَةِ، وَالاِخْتِلَافِ المَذْمُومِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَلِذَلِكَ فَادْعُ}</span> ... قُمْ بِالدَّعْوَةِ إِلَى ذَلِكَ الدِّينِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا حُجَّةَ بَيْنَنَا وَبَيْنَكُمُ}</span> ... لَا جِدَالَ بَيْنَنَا وَبَيْنَكُمْ؛ بَعْدَمَا تَبَيَّنَ الحَقُّ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
