<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُحَاجُّونَ فِي اللَّهِ}</span> ... يُخَاصِمُونَ فِي دِينِ اللهِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{دَاحِضَةٌ}</span> ... ذَاهِبَةٌ بَاطِلَةٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِالْحَقِّ}</span> ... بِالصِّدْقِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
